###  Summary Table

| Option Type                  |Black-Scholes Formula|Monte Carlo Formula                    |
| ---------------------------- |---------------------|---------------------------------------|
| European Call/Put            |  Exact              | Approximate                           |
| Asian Call/Put (Geometric)   |  Approximate        | Approximate (Geometric or Arithmetic) |
| American Call (no dividends) |  Same as European   | Approximate (LSM)                     |
| American Put                 |  No exact formula   | Approximate (LSM)                     |


